VHe sustained the same tenor in renderingSiddhivinayakam (Chamaram)andVandeham Jagadvallabham (Hamsadhvani),both prefixed and suffixed with invigoratingaalapanaandswaramin the two speed cycles. The rendering of theSriraga Pancharatna kriti Endaromahaanubhavuluof Thyagaraja surfacing all nuances of sublime expression embedded in thesahityaand the correspondingswaraksharasof the notation stood hailed as exemplary. Sustaining and extending the fervour further, he elaboratedSamajavaragamana (Hindolam)after enchantingly renderingEvaruraninuvina (Mohana)andSivasiva Anaraada (Pantuvarali)both adorned with knowledgeably knitaalapanaandswaram.The tail piece of the concert comprised compositions of Annamayya and Ramadas.Noted exponent of carnatic vocal S. Vasundharadevi, who was guest of honour, felicitated the artistes while VMDA Committee member Dr. P.V.C. Sarma introduced them.
